# Conductor "Files to copy" — https://www.conductor.build/docs/guides/use-files-to-copy
#
# Gitignored files that each new (local Mac) worktree needs. Only files that Git
# already ignores are copied. Cloud workspaces don't run Files to copy; the setup
# script in .conductor/settings.toml copies .env there instead.
#
# Adding this file replaces Conductor's default `.env*` pattern, so list every
# env file explicitly.
client/.env
client/.env.local
.env
